-- A2A Chairman Zuccoli Says Mediobanca Advising on Resolving Edison Dispute
-- Marco Bertacche
-- 2010-06-14T08:57:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-14/a2a-chairman-zuccoli-says-mediobanca-advising-on-resolving-edison-dispute.html

          
          
             A2A SpA Chairman Giuliano Zuccoli
said the utility has hired Mediobanca SpA to advise on Edison
SpA, the power company it controls with Electricite de France,
speaking to reporters in Milan today.  
 Intesa Sanpaolo SpA may hav a role in resolving the dispute
among Edison investors, Zuccoli said.  
          
          


  


        